OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sun 14 Jun to Tue 23 Jun
OL,6,FFine and dry across much of the UK for
OL,7,Fthe first couple of days of this
OL,8,Fperiod with long spells of sunshine
OL,9,Ffor most. Temperatures are likely to
OL,10,Fbe above normal and parts of the south
OL,11,Fcould be very warm for a time. A more
OL,12,Funsettled spell is likely through the
OL,13,Fmiddle of next week with outbreaks of
OL,14,Frain the north and northwest, some of
OL,15,Fwhich could spread to parts of the
OL,16,Fsouth and southeast at times. After
OL,17,Fthis, high pressure will probably
OL,18,Fbecome more dominant with conditions
OL,19,Fturning widely dry and settled, and
OL,20,Fprobably very warm for many.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
